I&#x27;m trying to implement links (both external and internal) in source code blocks in reStructuredText, but they are just rendered verbatim:

{code}
#!rst

.. sourcecode:: c++

    bool hello(`argtype <argtype_>`_ arg) const
{code}

But it just renders like this:

{code}
#!

bool hello(`argtype <argtype_>`_ arg) const
{code}

I&#x27;d be happy to forgo the syntax highlighting, just to have a shaded box the text goes in, how can I do that?
